<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="<%= locals.description %>" />
    <title><%= locals.title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h2>Welcome to USER REGISTRATION SYSTEM page</h2>
      <p>
        This is the basic "USER REGISTRATION SYSTEM" application. Which is built
        on Node.js and EJS. I have used PostgreSQL for database. It has
        functionalities of registration, login and logout.
      </p>
      <form action="/logout" method="get">
        <div class="input-box button">
          <input type="submit" value="Logout" />
        </div>
        <div class="text">
          <h3>
            If you want to delete your account, click delete.
            <a href="/delete">Delete Account</a>
          </h3>
          <a href="/">&larr; Back</a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
